Quincy. Here you go, buddy.
You're free.

07:34.620 --> 07:37.640
<i>DAN:</i>
<i>I slept with somebody else.</i>
<i>Someone...</i>

07:37.830 --> 07:40.110
- Uh...
- The one with the curly hair.

07:47.370 --> 07:49.860
[sighs] It's over now.

07:50.060 --> 07:51.130
- It's done.
- It's over?

07:51.330 --> 07:52.610
- It was a relationship?
- No.

07:52.810 --> 07:54.040
- Just a fuck?
- No. That's not what I was

07:54.240 --> 07:55.740
- trying to...
- More to it than fucking.

07:55.940 --> 07:56.780
I was trying to say that
it happened more than once.

07:56.980 --> 07:58.310
- That you fucked?
- Beth.

07:58.510 --> 08:00.480
Please, can you just
let me get this out?

08:00.680 --> 08:03.970
So, I have to hear it and you
get to decide how to tell me?

08:04.170 --> 08:05.710
Beth...

08:05.910 --> 08:08.750
You fucked someone else
more than once,

08:08.950 --> 08:11.230
- and now, it's over?
- Yes.

08:11.430 --> 08:13.150
I am so sorry.

08:13.350 --> 08:15.530
Why tonight?

08:17.840 --> 08:20.900
Why did I have to
be told tonight?

08:21.100 --> 08:23.200
Is it like a strategy?
Pile it all on,

08:23.400 --> 08:26.120
see how she reacts?

08:26.320 --> 08:28.340
[sighs]

08:28.540 --> 08:31.810
Was there really an emergency
at the jail that time?

08:34.330 --> 08:37.170
Why'd you have the cleaners
come ahead of schedule?

08:37.370 --> 08:38.830
That was not...

08:39.030 --> 08:41.350
That-that was...
Quincy actually got sick.

08:41.550 --> 08:43.790
That was not anything
to do with...

08:43.990 --> 08:45.620
How many times
is "more than once"?

08:45.820 --> 08:46.920
Four times.

08:47.120 --> 08:48.790
Ever in our house?

08:48.990 --> 08:51.140
- No. No, Beth.
- "No, Beth.

08:51.340 --> 08:54.700
No, I would never
do that to you."

08:57.140 --> 08:58.930
[clears throat]

08:59.130 --> 09:01.240
- When did it start?
- When you were away

09:01.440 --> 09:02.760
on the camping trip.

09:02.960 --> 09:05.510
You guys go to her place?

09:05.710 --> 09:07.030
Yes.

09:07.230 --> 09:09.340
And one time in the office.

09:09.530 --> 09:11.250
Does everyone there know?

09:11.450 --> 09:14.590
Does Mike know? Of course
your fucking fixer knows.

09:16.200 --> 09:18.340
You brought Quincy to her place?

09:18.540 --> 09:20.690
[sighs]

09:20.890 --> 09:22.740
Yes.

09:22.940 --> 09:24.260
Wow.

09:24.460 --> 09:26.350
- How did you know that?
- Quincy's mine.

09:26.550 --> 09:28.140
You gave me Quincy
for Christmas.

09:28.340 --> 09:30.570
Beth. Beth.

09:33.570 --> 09:35.670
Beth, I think
she was in our house.

09:35.870 --> 09:38.320
- What?
- I think that she was here.

09:38.520 --> 09:40.410
I don't know why she came.

09:40.610 --> 09:43.370
If it was to break something
or to steal something, but

09:43.570 --> 09:46.020
she is not a stable person.

09:47.410 --> 09:49.420
Right now, she is very angry

09:49.620 --> 09:52.600
that things did not turn out
the way that she wanted them to.

09:52.800 --> 09:54.420
And what?

09:54.620 --> 09:56.950
And I'm wondering
if maybe your mother

09:57.150 --> 09:58.380
surprised her,

09:58.580 --> 10:00.340
- maybe confronted her.
- What?

10:00.540 --> 10:03.000
I mean, are you... I...

10:03.200 --> 10:04.520
Do you hear yourself?

10:04.720 --> 10:06.650
I know how it sounds,

10:06.850 --> 10:08.660
but for our safety,

10:08.860 --> 10:09.870
all of our safety,

10:10.070 --> 10:11.570
we have to behave as though

10:11.770 --> 10:14.130
that's what happened
until we know that it didn't.

10:16.350 --> 10:18.230
'Cause this woman
is so obsessed with you

10:18.430 --> 10:19.970
she killed your mother-in-law,

10:20.170 --> 10:21.800
- that's what you think?
- I think it's possible.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.710
Yes.

10:23.910 --> 10:25.970
[laughs]

10:31.670 --> 10:32.980
[sniffles]

10:34.800 --> 10:36.940
So...

10:37.140 --> 10:39.690
I think this is probably it
for us, Dan.

10:39.890 --> 10:42.780
Do you realize that?

10:42.980 --> 10:46.130
I mean, I can't
take all this in.

10:46.330 --> 10:49.040
I think we're probably
already done.

10:49.240 --> 10:52.610
So, when my dad goes back
to his house in the morning,

10:52.810 --> 10:55.560
Ellen and I will go with him,
and we'll help him.

10:57.830 --> 10:59.580
[sniffles]

10:59.780 --> 11:01.060
And stay there.

11:01.260 --> 11:04.060
Don't come upstairs, okay?

11:04.260 --> 11:06.100
- Beth, can you just
hold on a sec...
- No.

11:06.300 --> 11:08.320
You want

11:08.520 --> 11:10.460
