MIKE:
She didn't. She wanted to know
if you knew that I was talking

11:29.110 --> 11:30.690
to her, and if Beth knew.

11:30.890 --> 11:33.260
- Like a threat?
- No, didn't seem like it.

11:33.460 --> 11:36.090
She said she felt like
Beth already did.

11:36.290 --> 11:38.010
Fuck.

11:38.210 --> 11:40.360
What the fuck
does that even mean?

11:40.560 --> 11:41.880
I...

11:42.080 --> 11:44.880
[sighs]

11:45.080 --> 11:47.100
She does know.

11:47.300 --> 11:48.450
Beth. I told her.

11:48.650 --> 11:51.540
- [sighs]
- Good for you, Danny. Yeah.

11:51.740 --> 11:54.020
Oh, Christ. Mikey,

11:54.220 --> 11:55.980
- was she in my goddamn house?
- I don't know.

11:56.180 --> 11:57.200
Which means yes.

11:57.400 --> 11:58.110
- Right?
- Yeah, probably yes.

11:58.310 --> 11:59.160
Probably yes.

11:59.360 --> 12:00.640
- Just...
- Fuck.

12:00.840 --> 12:02.460
