about any of this?

12:02.660 --> 12:04.860
Yes. I told her I was worried
it was a possibility.

12:05.060 --> 12:06.250
And?

12:06.450 --> 12:07.640
And she doesn't want
to hear it, Mike.

12:07.840 --> 12:08.990
She doesn't want me to say it.

12:09.190 --> 12:11.260
She doesn't want me
to repeat it.

12:11.460 --> 12:13.390
We got to do something now,
right? I mean, we have to.

12:13.590 --> 12:15.130
- We got to do something.
- Yeah, but first

12:15.330 --> 12:16.870
