that something is going to be.

12:17.070 --> 12:19.000
Even if all this with Sophie
is unrelated,

12:19.200 --> 12:20.610
we still got to think about it.

12:20.810 --> 12:22.880
I mean, she's definitely
thinking about it.

12:23.080 --> 12:25.400
Fuck. I got to get
a handle on her.

12:25.600 --> 12:27.190
I have not figured her out yet.

12:27.380 --> 12:29.930
Well, what if you don't?

12:30.130 --> 12:33.010
[sighs]
We could always kill her.

12:34.180 --> 12:36.460
Come on. Just, look,
we'll come up with something.

12:36.650 --> 12:38.070
Just for right now,
stay out of her way.

12:38.270 --> 12:39.880
Christ.

