<i>JULIA:</i>
<i>Where's Ellen?</i>

12:43.360 --> 12:45.940
- Should she be here?
- She should.

12:46.140 --> 12:47.470
You act like she listens to me.

12:47.670 --> 12:50.030
Ellen is, uh, watching <i>Stardust.</i>

12:50.230 --> 12:52.650
Okay. I brought beads.

12:52.840 --> 12:54.170
What do we think?

12:54.370 --> 12:57.000
I think she would be
totally into beads.

12:57.200 --> 12:58.700
Is Warren asleep?

12:58.890 --> 13:01.000
In the unconscious sense, yes.

13:01.200 --> 13:03.610
I also brought
a <i>Narnia</i>coloring book

13:03.810 --> 13:07.490
and a bath bomb
that has a necklace in it.

13:07.690 --> 13:10.490
- See you chumps in a few hours.
- Okay.

13:10.690 --> 13:13.570
I'll be right here. Okay.

13:16.750 --> 13:20.020
An actual fairy godmother.

13:20.220 --> 13:22.680
- Oh, God, I'm so sorry.
- [crying]

13:22.870 --> 13:25.110
I know, hon.

13:25.310 --> 13:28.770
Your mom, she was
a complicated woman,

13:28.970 --> 13:31.410
but I know she really
loved you a lot.

13:34.940 --> 13:36.250
It's Dan.

13:36.450 --> 13:37.650
What about him?

13:37.850 --> 13:39.210
He told me he was with
someone else.

13:39.410 --> 13:41.040
- What?
- A woman

13:41.240 --> 13:43.820
who works in his building.

13:46.300 --> 13:48.220
He said it was just a few times,

13:48.420 --> 13:50.400
