13:50.600 --> 13:51.970
Do you believe him?

13:52.170 --> 13:54.660
But he thinks that

13:54.860 --> 13:56.840
she came...

13:57.040 --> 13:58.840
to break in,

13:59.040 --> 14:00.410
steal things.

14:00.610 --> 14:01.930
That she didn't think
anyone was home,

14:02.130 --> 14:04.720
and that my mom...

14:04.920 --> 14:07.290
- surprised her or caught her
and surprised her.
- Wait, whoa, whoa, whoa, wait.

14:07.480 --> 14:09.550
What are you,
what are you saying?

14:09.750 --> 14:11.770
Is there any evidence? Is she...

14:11.970 --> 14:13.380
Is he having her arrested?

14:13.580 --> 14:15.080
I mean... [stammers]
he's a fucking prosecutor.

14:15.280 --> 14:17.600
Would he believe him?

14:17.800 --> 14:20.910
Look, I-I'm sorry.
Sorry, this isn't helping.

14:21.110 --> 14:23.520
So, what-what can I do?

14:23.720 --> 14:25.350
Don't tell anyone.

14:25.550 --> 14:26.650
- Especially...
- Oh...

14:26.850 --> 14:28.130
- Look, I'm...
- I don't want her

14:28.330 --> 14:30.260
to have anything else
in her head.

14:30.460 --> 14:32.880
I know, but Julia wouldn't
want you to, you know, decide

14:33.080 --> 14:34.270
she's not strong enough
to be your friend

14:34.470 --> 14:36.100
- when you need her most.
- I can't be strong

14:36.300 --> 14:38.010
if I think that
she's dealing with this

14:38.210 --> 14:41.890
on top of everything else.

14:42.080 --> 14:44.800
Just you.

14:45.000 --> 14:47.110
'Cause you're the dummy who said
to say the terrible things

14:47.310 --> 14:48.760
- out loud.
- [groans]

14:48.960 --> 14:51.760
Okay, so-so-so that's what
you don't want me to do.

14:51.960 --> 14:54.810
What can I do, though?

14:55.010 --> 14:57.340
- [sighs]
- Hmm?

14:57.530 --> 14:59.550
Nothing.

15:01.720 --> 15:03.780
What could you do?

15:03.980 --> 15:06.250
Make it so it didn't happen?

15:09.860 --> 15:11.730
You can't do anything.

