- Hey, skater buddy Ellen.
- Hey.

15:26.870 --> 15:28.630
Stella. I would've reached out
to you before,

15:28.830 --> 15:30.060
- but I didn't get your number.
- Oh, yeah.

15:30.260 --> 15:31.630
Thought I would
run into you before now.

15:31.830 --> 15:33.500
[chuckles] Did you see
the sign-up for Sky Zone?

15:33.700 --> 15:36.070
Um, yeah. You know, I did,
but I just... trampolines are

15:36.270 --> 15:37.800
- not my...
