Oh, that's not what
you were gonna say.

15:41.010 --> 15:42.820
[both laugh]

15:43.010 --> 15:44.470
What, you don't
like trampolines?

15:44.670 --> 15:46.730
Why? Fear of what? Freedom?

15:46.930 --> 15:49.950
- Flying? Awesomeness?
- Uh, wetting my pants in public.

15:50.150 --> 15:52.690
Oh, so wear
an Always Ultra Thin.

15:52.890 --> 15:55.830
Okay. [laughs] Um...

15:56.030 --> 15:57.480
- I can take a hint.
- [chuckles]

15:57.680 --> 15:59.220
Even if I like to make it
seem like I can't.

15:59.420 --> 16:01.010
Give me your number, though,

16:01.210 --> 16:03.400
for stuff besides
tramping. Cool?

16:03.600 --> 16:05.190
- Yeah.
- Here.

16:05.390 --> 16:07.710
Uh... [clears throat]

16:07.910 --> 16:09.060
Thank you. Okay.

16:09.260 --> 16:11.320
- Ellen what again?
- Uh, T-O-M-

16:11.520 --> 16:12.930
L-I-N-S-O-N.

16:13.130 --> 16:14.670
Oh, right, Ellen Tomlinson.

16:14.870 --> 16:16.800
Got you now.

16:18.620 --> 16:21.060
<i>- [bell dings]</i>
<i>- [elevator doors open]</i>

16:22.410 --> 16:23.980
[sighs]

16:26.720 --> 16:29.600
[sighs] Fuck.

16:29.800 --> 16:31.510
Dumbass.

16:34.640 --> 16:35.610
[elevator bell dings]

16:35.810 --> 16:37.170
Jesus

16:37.370 --> 16:39.520
- fucking Christ.
- Sorry. [chuckles]

16:41.000 --> 16:42.140
Hi.

16:42.340 --> 16:43.650
You took my keys.

16:48.350 --> 16:50.530
I just wanted to tell you
that I spoke to Mike.

16:54.270 --> 16:57.060
- Give me the keys, Alex.
- [chuckles]

16:57.260 --> 16:58.530
Of course.

17:00.140 --> 17:03.330
At first, I was,
I was a bit upset.

17:03.530 --> 17:04.770
I just, I didn't get why

17:04.970 --> 17:07.030
you couldn't come
speak to me yourself.

17:07.230 --> 17:09.900
But I get it now.

17:10.100 --> 17:11.370
[elevator buzzes]

17:13.110 --> 17:14.520
So, don't worry.

17:14.720 --> 17:16.810
I understand.

