that night I saw why.

36:56.950 --> 36:59.050
You're cleared, it's done.

36:59.250 --> 37:00.830
I still need to
fill Marcella in,

37:01.030 --> 37:03.830
but as far as I'm concerned,
the letter, the allegation

37:04.030 --> 37:05.750
