Jesus fucking Christ.

58:19.700 --> 58:20.540
Sorry.

58:21.840 --> 58:22.710
Hi.

58:24.060 --> 58:26.670
KEVIN:
<i>Episode 105 is bananas, right?</i>

58:27.320 --> 58:29.340
You come into it knowing

58:29.540 --> 58:31.210
that Alex
